    "description": "An exciting career opportunity awaits you at Vision Express India Asia Pacific Associates. We are on the lookout for a dedicated Marketplace Manager to strengthen our Indore-based team.\n\nAbout Vision Express India Asia Pacific Associates:\nVision Express India Asia Pacific Associates is a leading organization in the On-site sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Coordinate with vendors and suppliers for inventory management\n• Analyze sales data and customer behavior to drive revenue growth\n• Manage product listings, pricing, and promotions on the platform\n• Build and maintain affiliate and influencer marketing programs\n• Execute digital marketing campaigns across Google, Meta, and other channels\n• Develop and implement category growth strategies\n• Optimize product pages for search visibility and conversion\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• Chartered Accountant (ICAI)\n• 0-1 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in Product Management\n• Proficiency in Google Analytics\n• Proficiency in CRM Software\n• Proficiency in Performance Marketing\n• Proficiency in Magento\n• Proficiency in Customer Segmentation\n• Proficiency in MS Excel\n• Proficiency in Retention Marketing\n\nWork Mode: On-site - Work from our office\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Recognition and rewards programs\n• Modern office with recreational facilities\n• Meal coupons and food allowance\n• Employee stock options (ESOPs) for eligible roles\n• Annual performance appraisal\n• Company-sponsored certifications\n• Salary Range: 2.5 LPA - 6 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Indore, Madhya Pradesh, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with Vision Express India Asia Pacific Associates!",
